sections.content:
Introduction
2147 100 240 0714, or as commonly known by the Revolutionists as “Bean”. Bean is the main protagonist of Fractured by Time. Bean serves as the current leader of the Revolutionists with his partner Chilli. Bean works as a farmer when he is not doing his leadership duties at the Revolutionists.

Born on July 14, 2147 in Chicago to a lower class family. Bean has always faced challenges due to the class system by WISDOM, however he never really knew why. This all changed when he turned 10. At the age of 10 Bean was playing at the park when he noticed an old man needed help. Bean helped the man and in return the man told Bean that he was a veteran from the Apocalypse time. The man tells Bean everything about what happened in the past.

At the age of 16 Bean stumbles into a Revolutionist rally, in which he meets Chilli for the first time. While in the rally Bean learns about the motives of the Revolutionists, and feels a burning sensation inside him to want to help. At the age of 18 Bean joins the Revolutionists, it is also the time when he gets the name Bean. After 5 years of helping the Revolutionists with their missions, he is appointed leader of the Revolutionists at age 23.

Appearance
The name “Bean” was chosen as a homage to his reddish brown hair and his favorite food: beans. Additionally, Bean has a scar on top of his right eye due to a work related accident, which he keeps hidden with his long hair. Bean is always seen wearing work clothes as he finds them comfortable while working as a farmer and leading the Revolutionists. Bean is distinguished by his jade colored eyes that leave a lasting impression to those who meet him.

Personality
It's hard to describe a complex person like Bean, but perhaps most important is that he's lovable and dedicated. Of course he's also creative, modest and honorable. His loving nature though, this is what he's most popular for. Friends usually count on this and his contemplative nature when they're feeling down. Nobody's perfect of course and Bean has a range of flaws to deal with too. His obnoxious nature and dishonesty do cause plenty of friction and beyond what people are willing to deal with. Fortunately his dedication is usually there to help mend things when needed.
